sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant View as View Layer<br/>(personal-particular.blade.php)
    participant Controller as Controller Layer<br/>(Livewire Component)
    participant Auth as Auth Facade
    participant UserModel as User Model
    participant StudentModel as Student Model
    participant InstituteModel as Institute Model
    participant CampusModel as Campus Model
    participant ClassModel as Class Model
    participant DB as Database

    User->>View: Access /profile/personal-particular
    View->>Controller: Component initialization
    Controller->>Controller: mount()
    
    Controller->>Auth: user()
    Auth-->>Controller: User instance
    Controller->>UserModel: $user->student
    UserModel->>DB: SELECT * FROM students<br/>WHERE user_id = ?
    DB-->>UserModel: Student record
    UserModel-->>Controller: Student instance
    Controller->>Controller: Set $student property
    
    Controller-->>View: Render profile page
    View->>Auth: user()
    Auth-->>View: User instance (for display)
    
    View->>UserModel: Access user properties
    UserModel-->>View: username, chinese_name,<br/>family_name, given_name
    
    View->>StudentModel: $student->institute
    StudentModel->>DB: Eager load institute relationship
    DB-->>StudentModel: Institute record
    StudentModel->>InstituteModel: Get institute data
    InstituteModel-->>StudentModel: Institute instance
    StudentModel-->>View: Institute name
    
    View->>StudentModel: $student->campus
    StudentModel->>DB: Eager load campus relationship
    DB-->>StudentModel: Campus record
    StudentModel->>CampusModel: Get campus data
    CampusModel-->>StudentModel: Campus instance
    StudentModel-->>View: Campus name
    
    View->>StudentModel: $student->classes()
    StudentModel->>DB: SELECT * FROM classes<br/>WHERE student_id = ?<br/>ORDER BY academic_year DESC
    DB-->>StudentModel: Class records
    StudentModel->>ClassModel: Get first() class
    ClassModel-->>StudentModel: Latest class instance
    StudentModel-->>View: Current class code
    
    View->>StudentModel: Access student properties
    StudentModel-->>View: gender, date_of_birth, nationality,<br/>mother_tongue, tel_no, mobile_no, address
    
    View->>UserModel: $user->avatar
    UserModel-->>View: Avatar URL
    
    View-->>User: Display personal information:<br/>- Student ID<br/>- Names (Chinese, Family, Given)<br/>- Institute & Campus<br/>- Current Class<br/>- Personal details<br/>- Contact information<br/>- Student photo
